            , were indicted for <rs id="t18101205-3-off11" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18101205-3-off11" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18101205-3-off11" type="offenceSubcategory" value="housebreaking"></interp>
               feloniously breaking and entering the dwelling-house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18101205-3-victim66" type="victimName">
                           Frances 
                           Clarke
                        <interp inst="t18101205-3-victim66" type="surname" value="Clarke"></interp>
