                        <interp inst="t18101205-3-person67" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                     </persName>
                  , and others of the family then and there being, and feloniously stealing, a pair of silk stockings, value 14 s. the property of 
                     <persName id="t18101205-3-person68">
                        Frances 
                        Clarke
                     <interp inst="t18101205-3-person68" type="surname" value="Clarke"></interp>
